de.btu.openinfra.backend.db.pojos.solr

Class SolrComplexQueryPartPojo

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.btu.openinfra.backend.db.pojos.OpenInfraPojo
      • de.btu.openinfra.backend.db.pojos.solr.SolrComplexQueryPartPojo

  • public class SolrComplexQueryPartPojo
extends OpenInfraPojo
    This POJO is a container for a part of the complex search query that is generated by the extended search. TODO The POJOs must extend OpenInfraPojo to be accessible for the primer class. The UUID and TRID that is provided by the OpenInfraPojo will never be used.
    Author:
    BTU DBIS
